def heart_disease(row):
    if row == 0:
        return 'Absence'
    elif row == 1:
        return 'Presence'
In [11]:

In [24]:
def age_range(row):
    if row>=29 and row<40:
        return 'Young age'
    elif row>=40 and row<55:
        return 'Middle age'
    else:
        return 'Elder age'
In [25]:
df['Age_range']=df['age'].apply(age_range)
